<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_439" id="219r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_439_r1l13"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Pernegk<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Kulmach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_439_r1l14"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt vvie Jr mit vns <expan>cʒered<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l15">habt etwas <expan>ernſtlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache vnd begert daʒ vvir ew ein 
<del rend="strikethrough">geleitt </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l16">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> ſıcher <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> geleitt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ynwendig vnd awſwendıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l17"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / . Alſo <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l18">wir ew vnſer geleıtte <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd awſgeen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l19">veirtag /. vnd <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>germeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l20"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> hören / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_439" id="219r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Pernegk<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Kulmach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie ir mit uns
                            <expan>cze red<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt etwas
                            <expan>ernstlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache und begert, daz wir ew ein
                        sicher <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> geleitt
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ynwendig und awswendig
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
                        Also <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew unser geleitte
                        <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">awsgeen
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ost<ex>er</ex>veirtag</q>06.04.1412</note></app> und
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>germeist<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr rede
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> hören. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
